tafsir[1]{c,v,t}:
  5,73,"One who submits to God finds that he has to face all kinds of difficulties in this life. His worldly hopes and ambitions will not necessarily be fulfilled. Yet one who is firm in the faith will not be put off by adversity he will persevere, making sure that he leaves this world as a believer, so that he can look forward to God’s blessings in the next world."